%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Only the Guild Leaders may apply for a guild add-on.  There are many things that may be bought with, or updated in your guild, but is not included in the guild price.  The payment for the additions to your guild will be taken straight from your guild treasury only.  Major guild add-ons will happen twice a year; during this time each guild will get 1 week where they can have guild changes and updates.  If there are any questions, ask the Guild Immortal.%^RESET%^

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^The prices for guild add-ons are as follows:%^RESET%^

%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Extra Room: %^WHITE%^200,000 Gold%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^Just plain rooms.  (Does not contain a board) %^RESET%^

