        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^of a guild member. %^RESET%^

%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Class Halls: %^WHITE%^300,000k Gold%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^This is per class hall, and the hall would allow you to train, level, %^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^and up all skills and stats. %^RESET%^

%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Shop: %^WHITE%^400,000 Gold%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^This price is per shop.  Shops can sell vital healers, armour, weapons,%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^or other objects. %^RESET%^
	%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^*%^RED%^Note%^WHITE%^* %^RED%^Vital healers may eventually be eliminated from the game. %^RESET%^

%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Guild Gear: %^WHITE%^100,000 Gold%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^This price is per item. Guild gear constitutes weapons, armour, and %^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^items.  In order to buy guild gear you must have a shop.  All guilds%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^are NOT allowed to have any elite items; however, they will be allowed%^RESET%^
        %^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^to have hm items, as well as 1 item that has a special.%^RESET%^
%^BOLD%^%^RED%^Special Item Guildlines: %^RESET%^
